      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a reliable source for parts? This vehicle is ready for its next adventure! While it is currently in poor condition and will require some mechanical work and cosmetic repairs, it presents a fantastic opportunity for a DIY enthusiast or someone looking for a great value. It's a solid foundation waiting for a little TLC to get back on the road!",
