    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she's a total beauty. This car is in seriously incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this thing since day one, keeping it spotless and perfectly maintained. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here; it's practically flawless. I\u2019m looking for a new home for it where it'll be just as loved. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, exhibiting flawless VANOS operation and documented rod bearing service. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with no fatigue at the rear subframe mounting points. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the car maintains its factory-spec damping and bushings, offering the precise, communicative turn-in that defined the M-division's golden era. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history available. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
