    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint is in showroom condition, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no stone chips, swirl marks, or scratches. Inside, the cabin is immaculate and smoke-free, with the premium leather upholstery showing zero bolster wear and retaining its original factory scent. Every electronic feature and mechanical component operates flawlessly, backed by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history performed exclusively at the main dealership. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched alloy wheels wrapped in fresh performance rubber, this car is a 'time capsule' example for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
